manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: WH08X32697 Washer Door Lid Lock Switch: Package Includes: 1x Washer Door Lid Lock Switch

PRODUCT INFORMATION: Replacement Parts Number: WH01X24114, WH01X26114, WH01X27954, WH08X31577.Compatible Brands: General Electric, Hotpoint. HIGH QUALITY: The Washing machine lid lock switch is made of high quality material, heat resistance, wear resistance, more durable and have a longer service life. PRODUCT INSTALLATION: The door lid lock switch WH01X27954 is easy to install, no special tools are required, remove the old lid lock and replace new WH01X27954 Door Lock Switch. Please disconnect the electrical power supply before install and Wear work gloves to protect your hands. You can get your washer back up and running again by this replacement part.

Multiple Functions: Washer Lid Lock Switch WH01X27954 prevents the washer lid from opening during the wash cycle and spin cycle. Fix the following symptoms: Will Not Start Will not drain Will not agitate Lid or door won’t close
